# BioThings Explorer TRAPI Query Graph Handler

A on-the-fly query engine for BioThings Explorer based on TRAPI Query Graph.

[![Test Coveralls](https://github.com/biothings/bte_trapi_query_graph_handler/actions/workflows/coverage.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/biothings/bte_trapi_query_graph_handler/actions/workflows/coverage.yml)
[![Coverage Status](https://coveralls.io/repos/github/biothings/bte_trapi_query_graph_handler/badge.svg?branch=main)](https://coveralls.io/github/biothings/bte_trapi_query_graph_handler?branch=main)

## Install

```bash
npm i @biothings-explorer/query_graph_handler
```

## Usage

### Making a single hop query

```javascript
const handler = require("@biothings-explorer/query_graph_handler");
const queryHandler = new handler.TRAPIQueryHandler();
const oneHopQuery = {
    "workflow": [
        {"id": "lookup"}
    ],
    "message": {
        "query_graph": {
            "edges": {
                "e00": {
                    "object": "n01",
                    "subject": "n00",
                    "predicates": ["biolink:functional_association"]
                }
            },
            "nodes": {
                "n00": {
                    "categories": ["biolink:Gene"],
                    "ids": ["ENSEMBL:ENSG00000123374"]
                },
                "n01": {
                    "categories": ["biolink:BiologicalProcess"]
                }
            }
        }
    }
};
queryHandler.setQueryGraph(OneHopQuery);
await queryHandler.query();
console.log(queryHandler.getResponse())
```

    "workflow": [
        {"id": "lookup"}
    ],
    "message": {
        "query_graph": {
            "nodes": {
                "n0": {
                    "categories": ["biolink:Disease"],
                    "ids": ["MONDO:0005737"]
                },
                "n1": {
                    "categories": ["biolink:Gene"]
                },
                "n2": {
                    "categories": ["biolink:SmallMolecule"]
                }
            },
            "edges": {
                "e01": {
                    "subject": "n0",
                    "object": "n1"
                },
                "e02": {
                    "subject": "n1",
                    "object": "n2"
                }
            }
        }
    }

queryHandler.setQueryGraph(multiHopQuery);

const handler = require("@biothings-explorer/query_graph_handler");

const multiPredicatesQuery = {
    "workflow": [
        {"id": "lookup"}
    ],
    "message": {
        "query_graph": {
            "nodes": {
                "n0": {
                    "categories": ["biolink:Disease"],
                    "ids": ["MONDO:0005737"]
                },
                "n1": {
                    "categories": ["biolink:SmallMolecule"]
                }
            },
            "edges": {
                "e01": {
                    "subject": "n0",
                    "object": "n1",
                    "predicates": ["biolink:treated_by", "biolink:affected_by"]
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
queryHandler.setQueryGraph(multiPredicatesQuery);
await queryHandler.query();
